{"name":"Dancing Lights","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You create up to four torch-sized lights within range, making them appear as torches, lanterns, or glowing orbs that hover in the air for the duration. You can also combine the four lights into one glowing vaguely humanoid form of Medium size. Whichever form you choose, each light sheds dim light in a 10-foot radius.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>As a bonus action on your turn, you can move the lights up to 60 feet to a new spot within range. A light must be within 20 feet of another light created by this spell, and a light winks out if it exceeds the spell's range.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"space"},"range":{"value":120,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":0,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"a bit of phosphorus or wychwood, or a glowworm","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"always","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/magic/light/orbs-firefly-hand-yellow.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"dancing%20lights_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.mysB3YYLD3FhGlYN"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835810679,"modifiedTime":1673836307864,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"L8IglAVpE72mpSkl"}
{"name":"Cause Fear","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You awaken the sense of mortality in one creature you can see within range. A construct or an undead is immune to this effect. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or become @condition[frightened] of you until the spell ends. The @condition[frightened] target can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> <p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, you can target one additional creature for each slot level above 1st. The creatures must be within 30 feet of each other when you target them.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"nec","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/commodities/bones/skull-hollow-worn-blue.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"XGE","hash":"cause%20fear_xge","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.XEdQwHDc6DCvIOtO"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835747416,"modifiedTime":1673836309404,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"9SUMZuyHMewgwR3o"}
{"name":"Compelled Duel","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You attempt to compel a creature into a duel. One creature that you can see within range must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, the creature is drawn to you, compelled by your divine demand. For the duration, it has disadvantage on attack rolls against creatures other than you, and must make a Wisdom saving throw each time it attempts to move to a space that is more than 30 feet away from you; if it succeeds on this saving throw, this spell doesn't restrict the target's movement for that turn.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>The spell ends if you attack any other creature, if you cast a spell that targets a hostile creature other than the target, if a creature friendly to you damages the target or casts a harmful spell on it, or if you end your turn more than 30 feet away from the target.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"enc","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-stake-gray.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"compelled%20duel_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.nAkwV5w2fClt5ypt"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835757570,"modifiedTime":1673836310716,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"ZWJeJPtXPxEjOvxn"}
{"name":"Detect Evil and Good","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>For the duration, you know if there is an aberration, celestial, elemental, fey, fiend, or undead within 30 feet of you, as well as where the creature is located. Similarly, you know if there is a place or object within 30 feet of you that has been magically consecrated or desecrated.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>The spell can penetrate most barriers, but it is blocked by 1 foot of stone, 1 inch of common metal, a thin sheet of lead, or 3 feet of wood or dirt.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"div","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/magic/time/day-night-sun-moon.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"detect%20evil%20and%20good_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.bCJ1btOUE2zHmzKS"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835820533,"modifiedTime":1673836311946,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"DNvkpnkyOajx0LXL"}
{"name":"Detect Magic","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>For the duration, you sense the presence of magic within 30 feet of you. If you sense magic in this way, you can use your action to see a faint aura around any visible creature or object in the area that bears magic, and you learn its <span class=\"bold\">school of magic</span>, if any.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>The spell can penetrate most barriers, but it is blocked by 1 foot of stone, 1 inch of common metal, a thin sheet of lead, or 3 feet of wood or dirt.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"div","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":true,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/magic/unholy/hands-cloud-light-pink.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"detect%20magic_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.rCdda3QU0A2uPMG4"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835829319,"modifiedTime":1673836313631,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"8VBcSYBIkXJIlaXl"}
{"name":"Detect Poison and Disease","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>For the duration, you can sense the presence and location of poisons, poisonous creatures, and diseases within 30 feet of you. You also identify the kind of poison, poisonous creature, or disease in each case.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>The spell can penetrate most barriers, but it is blocked by 1 foot of stone, 1 inch of common metal, a thin sheet of lead, or 3 feet of wood or dirt.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"div","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":true,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"a yew leaf","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/skills/toxins/poison-bottle-open-fire-purple.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"detect%20poison%20and%20disease_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.lCAYLX9br7PievV2"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835837085,"modifiedTime":1673836314807,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"28XV9YuIRln7U9Nt"}
{"name":"Silent Image","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You create the image of an object, a creature, or some other visible phenomenon that is no larger than a 15-foot cube. The image appears at a spot within range and lasts for the duration. The image is purely visual; it isn't accompanied by sound, smell, or other sensory effects.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>You can use your action to cause the image to move to any spot within range. As the image changes location, you can alter its appearance so that its movements appear natural for the image. For example, if you create an image of a creature and move it, you can alter the image so that it appears to be walking.</p><p>Physical interaction with the image reveals it to be an illusion, because things can pass through it. A creature that uses its action to examine the image can determine that it is an illusion with a successful Intelligence (@skill[Investigation]) check against your spell save DC. If a creature discerns the illusion for what it is, the creature can see through the image.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":15,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cube"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"ill","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"a bit of fleece","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/commodities/treasure/crystal-pedastal-red-gold.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"silent%20image_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.RriVVRvrVQB1vo2x"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835884174,"modifiedTime":1673836315973,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"CUrUbZGPYiLh88IC"}
{"name":"Witch Bolt","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>A beam of crackling, blue energy lances out toward a creature within range, forming a sustained arc of lightning between you and the target. Make a ranged spell attack against that creature. On a hit, the target takes [[/r 1d12]] lightning damage, and on each of your turns for the duration, you can use your action to deal [[/r 1d12]] lightning damage to the target automatically. The spell ends if you use your action to do anything else. The spell also ends if the target is ever outside the spell's range or if it has total cover from you.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"8\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> <p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the initial damage increases by [[/r 1d12]] for each slot level above 1st.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"rsak","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d12","lightning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"a twig from a tree that has been struck by lightning","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"1d12"}},"img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-sparks-purple.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"witch%20bolt_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.92fS2DUb1ia6FhK5"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835910007,"modifiedTime":1673836317478,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"fD3pjgeQ8rCGJoLI"}
{"name":"Zephyr Strike","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You move like the wind. Until the spell ends, your movement doesn't provoke opportunity attacks.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>Once before the spell ends, you can give yourself advantage on one weapon attack roll on your turn. That attack deals an extra [[/r 1d8]] force damage on a hit. Whether you hit or miss, your walking speed increases by 30 feet until the end of that turn.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"trs","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/skills/melee/blade-tips-double-blue.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"XGE","hash":"zephyr%20strike_xge","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.XDrbOq5mR7UoO1BV"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835917397,"modifiedTime":1673836319035,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"MrkdivHMWaf4ir1F"}
{"name":"Crown of Madness","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>One humanoid of your choice that you can see within range must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or become @condition[charmed] by you for the duration. While the target is @condition[charmed] in this way, a twisted crown of jagged iron appears on its head, and a madness glows in its eyes.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>The @condition[charmed] target must use its action before moving on each of its turns to make a melee attack against a creature other than itself that you mentally choose. The target can act normally on its turn if you choose no creature or if none are within its reach.</p><p>On your subsequent turns, you must use your action to maintain control over the target, or the spell ends. Also, the target can make a Wisdom saving throw at the end of each of its turns. On a success, the spell ends.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":120,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"enc","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-barbute-horned-gold-red.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"crown%20of%20madness_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.z7AcZLfNePj3dPvV"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835766571,"modifiedTime":1673836321746,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"kOmm6ffnEGKlAiSE"}
{"name":"Alter Self","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You assume a different form. When you cast the spell, choose one of the following options, the effects of which last for the duration of the spell. While the spell lasts, you can end one option as an action to gain the benefits of a different one.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"2\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Aquatic Adaptation.</span></span> <p>You adapt your body to an aquatic environment, sprouting gills and growing webbing between your fingers. You can breathe underwater and gain a swimming speed equal to your walking speed.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Change Appearance.</span></span> <p>You transform your appearance. You decide what you look like, including your height, weight, facial features, sound of your voice, hair length, coloration, and distinguishing characteristics, if any. You can make yourself appear as a member of another race, though none of your statistics change. You also can't appear as a creature of a different size than you, and your basic shape stays the same; if you're bipedal, you can't use this spell to become quadrupedal, for instance. At any time for the duration of the spell, you can use your action to change your appearance in this way again.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"4\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Natural Weapons.</span></span> <p>You grow claws, fangs, spines, horns, or a different natural weapon of your choice. Your unarmed strikes deal [[/r 1d6]] bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing damage, as appropriate to the natural weapon you chose, and you are proficient with your unarmed strikes. Finally, the natural weapon is magic and you have a +1 bonus to the attack and damage rolls you make using it.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"trs","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/creatures/claws/pincer-crab-brown.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"alter%20self_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.mAvnNYqcBLwYWUQc"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835786044,"modifiedTime":1673836323159,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"E7Qa1UYRGSZDROot"}
{"name":"Barkskin","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You touch a willing creature. Until the spell ends, the target's skin has a rough, bark-like appearance, and the target's AC can't be less than 16, regardless of what kind of armor it is wearing.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"touch","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"trs","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"a handful of oak bark","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/magic/nature/barrier-shield-wood-vines.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"barkskin_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.1wzr0xRdFLxX0zg7"}},"effects":[{"_id":"uM6rgctYpcbCVSkn","flags":{},"changes":[{"key":"system.attributes.ac.formula","value":"16","mode":5,"priority":null},{"key":"system.attributes.ac.calc","value":"custom","mode":5,"priority":null}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":3600,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"icons/magic/nature/barrier-shield-wood-vines.webp","label":"Barkskin","origin":"Item.VQMKMnQDw5rzL0zp","tint":null,"transfer":false}],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835792021,"modifiedTime":1673836325061,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"bdWi6KTyHKCL1tjt"}
{"name":"Beast Sense","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You touch a willing beast. For the duration of the spell, you can use your action to see through the beast's eyes and hear what it hears, and continue to do so until you use your action to return to your normal senses. While perceiving through the beast's senses, you gain the benefits of any special senses possessed by that creature, though you are @condition[blinded] and @condition[deafened] to your own surroundings.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"touch","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"div","components":{"value":"","vocal":false,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":true,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-eye.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"beast%20sense_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.DG1ZGY39nt5xpNBG"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835798998,"modifiedTime":1673836326991,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"2ArZ6fPzWoaT41xo"}
{"name":"Flame Blade","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You evoke a fiery blade in your free hand. The blade is similar in size and shape to a scimitar, and it lasts for the duration. If you let go of the blade, it disappears, but you can evoke the blade again as a bonus action.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>You can use your action to make a melee spell attack with the fiery blade. On a hit, the target takes [[/r 3d6]] fire damage.</p><p>The flaming blade sheds bright light in a 10-foot radius and dim light for an additional 10 feet.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"6\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> <p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 1d6]] for every two slot levels above 2nd.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"msak","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["(floor((@item.level) / 2) + 2)d6","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"leaf of sumac","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/magic/fire/dagger-rune-enchant-flame-strong-orange.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"flame%20blade_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.gJ63dC695s45Xkuk"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835857110,"modifiedTime":1673836328443,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"H609SXPIK1dEbYrA"}
{"name":"Ray of Enfeeblement","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>A black beam of enervating energy springs from your finger toward a creature within range. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, the target deals only half damage with weapon attacks that use Strength until the spell ends.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>At the end of each of the target's turns, it can make a Constitution saving throw against the spell. On a success, the spell ends.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"rsak","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"nec","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/creatures/magical/humanoid-silhouette-glowing-pink.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"ray%20of%20enfeeblement_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.hcfmrB696ZpAzZfb"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835870171,"modifiedTime":1673836329948,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"zQ8oPM3dKQSg9kSh"}
{"name":"Shadow Blade","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You weave together threads of shadow to create a sword of solidified gloom in your hand. This magic sword lasts until the spell ends. It counts as a simple melee weapon with which you are proficient. It deals [[/r 2d8]] psychic damage on a hit and has the finesse, light, and thrown properties (range 20/60). In addition, when you use the sword to attack a target that is in dim light or darkness, you make the attack roll with advantage.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>If you drop the weapon or throw it, it dissipates at the end of the turn. Thereafter, while the spell persists, you can use a bonus action to cause the sword to reappear in your hand.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"7\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> <p>When you cast this spell using a 3rd- or 4th-level spell slot, the damage increases to [[/r 3d8]]. When you cast it using a 5th- or 6th-level spell slot, the damage increases to [[/r 4d8]]. When you cast it using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the damage increases to [[/r 5d8]].</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d8","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"ill","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/skills/melee/sword-stuck-glowing-pink.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"XGE","hash":"shadow%20blade_xge","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.NF2MxkAHONYzxQ3U"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835877840,"modifiedTime":1673836336269,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"RYEjqh5tIS4BhmJe"}
{"name":"Skywrite","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You cause up to ten words to form in a part of the sky you can see. The words appear to be made of cloud and remain in place for the spell's duration. The words dissipate when the spell ends. A strong wind can disperse the clouds and end the spell early.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":""},"range":{"value":0,"long":null,"units":"spec"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"trs","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":true,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/magic/light/projectile-flare-blue.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"XGE","hash":"skywrite_xge","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.VdMZ3jARDwhQaXYc"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835890845,"modifiedTime":1673836338129,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"EGJN9KWsbddUW66x"}
{"name":"Stoneskin","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>This spell turns the flesh of a willing creature you touch as hard as stone. Until the spell ends, the target has resistance to nonmagical bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"touch","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":4,"school":"abj","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"diamond dust worth 100 gp, which the spell consumes","consumed":true,"cost":100,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/magic/earth/strike-fist-stone-gray.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"stoneskin_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.IX5QfAa9rOXU50sj"}},"effects":[{"label":"Stoneskin","icon":"icons/magic/earth/strike-fist-stone-gray.webp","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e.spells.ReMbjfeOKoSj3O79","duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":3600,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"disabled":false,"_id":"cSVCA9h5OEo5lfBE","changes":[{"key":"system.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"bludgeoning","priority":null},{"key":"system.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"piercing","priority":null},{"key":"system.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"slashing","priority":null},{"key":"system.traits.dr.bypasses","mode":2,"value":"mgc","priority":null}],"tint":null,"transfer":false,"flags":{}}],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835902614,"modifiedTime":1673836339802,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"QCnu02ZKnhDgUEQb"}
{"name":"Enervation","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>A tendril of inky darkness reaches out from you, touching a creature you can see within range to drain life from it. The target must make a Dexterity saving throw. On a successful save, the target takes [[/r 2d8]] necrotic damage, and the spell ends. On a failed save, the target takes [[/r 4d8]] necrotic damage, and until the spell ends, you can use your action on each of your turns to automatically deal [[/r 4d8]] necrotic damage to the target. The spell ends if you use your action to do anything else, if the target is ever outside the spell's range, or if the target has total cover from you.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>Whenever the spell deals damage to a target, you regain hit points equal to half the amount of necrotic damage the target takes.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"5\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> <p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 6th level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 1d8]] for each slot level above 5th.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d8","necrotic"],["4d8","necrotic"],["4d8","necrotic"],["","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":5,"school":"nec","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"1d8"}},"img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-life-soul-green.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"XGE","hash":"enervation_xge","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.sCiIrmV4nyv0dIky"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835842780,"modifiedTime":1673836342060,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"gT4of2XAEKSOA2oj"}
{"name":"Immolation","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Flames wreathe one creature you can see within range. The target must make a Dexterity saving throw. It takes [[/r 8d6]] fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. On a failed save, the target also burns for the spell's duration. The burning target sheds bright light in a 30-foot radius and dim light for an additional 30 feet. At the end of each of its turns, the target repeats the saving throw. It takes [[/r 4d6]] fire damage on a failed save, and the spell ends on a successful one. These magical flames can't be extinguished by nonmagical means.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>If damage from this spell kills a target, the target is turned to ash.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":90,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["8d6","fire"],["4d6","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":5,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/magic/death/projectile-skull-fire-orange.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"XGE","hash":"immolation_xge","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.38GkRTKhfkd4He9d"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835863836,"modifiedTime":1673836343618,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"VrRnCmZeUSErLjvd"}
{"name":"Find the Path","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>This spell allows you to find the shortest, most direct physical route to a specific fixed location that you are familiar with on the same plane of existence. If you name a destination on another plane of existence, a destination that moves (such as a mobile fortress), or a destination that isn't specific (such as \"a green dragon's lair\"), the spell fails.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>For the duration, as long as you are on the same plane of existence as the destination, you know how far it is and in what direction it lies. While you are traveling there, whenever you are presented with a choice of paths along the way, you automatically determine which path is the shortest and most direct route (but not necessarily the safest route) to the destination.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"minute","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"day"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":6,"school":"div","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"a set of divinatory tools—such as bones, ivory sticks, cards, teeth, or carved runes—worth 100 gp and an object from the location you wish to find","consumed":false,"cost":100,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/environment/wilderness/terrain-river-road-gray.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"find%20the%20path_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.Y0WWqO8mSyHWscUq"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673835849659,"modifiedTime":1673836345370,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"5b3SaE3BcftpM5uE"}
{"name":"Divine Favor","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Your prayer empowers you with divine radiance. Until the spell ends, your weapon attacks deal an extra [[/r 1d4]] radiant damage on a hit.</p><p>This spell can not be cast on a weapon or piece of ammunition already under the effects of a spell.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><p></p></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4","radiant"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/skills/ranged/wand-attack-beam-blue.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"divine%20favor_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.Og0XMhS0ajilB6vA"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673836397955,"modifiedTime":1673837327093,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"lKGU0wdNV4wMsAZj"}
{"name":"Ensnaring Strike","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The next time you hit a creature with a weapon attack before this spell ends, a writhing mass of thorny vines appears at the point of impact, and the target must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be @condition[restrained] by the magical vines until the spell ends. A Large or larger creature has advantage on this saving throw. If the target succeeds on the save, the vines shrivel away.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><p></p></div><p>While @condition[restrained] by this spell, the target takes [[/r 1d6]] piercing damage at the start of each of its turns. A creature @condition[restrained] by the vines or one that can touch the creature can use its action to make a Strength check against your spell save DC. On a success, the target is freed.</p><p>This spell can not be cast on a weapon or piece of ammunition already under the effects of a spell.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span class=\"entry-title-inner\"><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></span></p><p>If you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 1d6]] for each slot level above 1st.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><p></p></div></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><p></p></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"str","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"con","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"1d6"}},"img":"icons/magic/nature/root-vine-hand-strike.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"ensnaring%20strike_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.Agom35rP1WTL7vKZ"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673836414765,"modifiedTime":1673837330358,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"Nw4fMytm5hFzHxP5"}
{"name":"Hail of Thorns","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The next time you hit a creature with a ranged weapon attack before the spell ends, this spell creates a rain of thorns that sprouts from your ranged weapon or ammunition. In addition to the normal effect of the attack, the target of the attack and each creature within 5 feet of it must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes [[/r 1d10]] piercing damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p>This spell can not be cast on a weapon or piece of ammunition already under the effects of a spell.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><p><span class=\"entry-title-inner\"><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></span></p><p>If you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 1d10]] for each slot level above 1st (to a maximum of [[/r 6d10]]).</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><p></p></div></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><p></p></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d10","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"con","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"1d10"}},"img":"icons/magic/nature/root-vine-spiral-thorns-teal.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"hail%20of%20thorns_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.4skvV9BlvGCv82PI"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673836431692,"modifiedTime":1673837333768,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"3sBrT62G3hVBjAfC"}
{"name":"Searing Smite","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The next time you hit a creature with a melee weapon attack during the spell's duration, your weapon flares with white-hot intensity, and the attack deals an extra [[/r 1d6]] fire damage to the target and causes the target to ignite in flames. At the start of each of its turns until the spell ends, the target must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, it takes [[/r 1d6]] fire damage. On a successful save, the spell ends. If the target or a creature within 5 feet of it uses an action to put out the flames, or if some other effect douses the flames (such as the target being submerged in water), the spell ends.</p><p>This spell can not be cast on a weapon or piece of ammunition already under the effects of a spell.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><p><span class=\"entry-title-inner\"><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></span></p><p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the initial extra damage dealt by the attack increases by [[/r 1d6]] for each slot level above 1st.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><p></p></div></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><p></p></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","fire"],["1d6","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"1d6"}},"img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-hammer-destructive-orange.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"searing%20smite_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.WMwU0Yj89h5vjZnE"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673836461966,"modifiedTime":1673837334769,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O":3},"_id":"lzcSPXv79uJ3M2zV"}
{"name":"Thunderous Smite","type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The first time you hit with a melee weapon attack during this spell's duration, your weapon rings with thunder that is audible within 300 feet of you, and the attack deals an extra [[/r 2d6]] thunder damage to the target. Additionally, if the target is a creature, it must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be pushed 10 feet away from you and knocked @condition[prone].</p><p>This spell can not be cast on a weapon or piece of ammunition already under the effects of a spell.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><p></p></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d6","thunder"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"str","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-wide-white.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"spells.html","source":"PHB","hash":"thunderous%20smite_phb","propDroppable":"spell"},"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.N8zPGXkolwwuRToI.Item.bgSqgvxeaJUB7zPV"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673836479302,"modifiedTime":1673837336027,"lastModifiedBy":"CVptjiALjBpsCb5O"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CVptjiALj